Comment: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other song sound effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.80,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Slowly, quietly, floating by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:47.52,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}Gently fading into the distant bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:56.36,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}More fickle than the wind,\N my goal is beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.45,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Let's go together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:05.12,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and skip along,\N the world's spring breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.67,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun brings all our smiles together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:18.22,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Between "good morning" and "good bye" it's just us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:21.85,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}We can do whatever we want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:27.98,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}The sunlight shining down,\N a brand new sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:33.69,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning arch we promised to meet at
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:41.49,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Waving your hand at me,\N let me make today a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.62,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Let's start by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:48.10,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like they'd reach, but I know they just won't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:55.52,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I need? What don't I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:16.29,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to look, I already know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:23.38,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little courage and a push
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:27.26,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(I miss you) If I called you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.77,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(do you hear me) I could meet your voice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:34.35,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(hold me real tight) But I want to hold you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.90,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(don't you feel me) I might just die if I did
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:41.40,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(I miss you) I want to see you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:45.07,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,(this ain't right) It's not exactly what you'd call love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:48.53,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,But without you there's just no point
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:54.50,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to hold you tight (never get enough)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:45.92,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Next to me in the sunset, a silhouette tall as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:54.76,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of another fun day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:01.90,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got so much unending stuff to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:09.24,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time for us to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:16.41,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, I'll text you later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:23.71,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's page is about all our smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:31.01,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, thanks as always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:39.56,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we could be together today too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:46.73,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Humhumhum, the wind and my heart are humming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:53.99,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}At the next corner, I'll turn around and say "Bye bye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you wearing your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'm completely awake right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, carbonation is the best way to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually it's coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This bubbling feeling makes me blink and wake up in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:17.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:26.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you know, I haven't seen Tooru at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has day duty today, so she'll be busy all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:34.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? It feels like she's always with us. It's kind of quiet without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. But day duty is day duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you feel like seeing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,First years. And Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs70\fad(400,0)\pos(640,220)\c&HE9F0F7&\be4}Classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look! These scribbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're carved into the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it feels like forever since we were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't too long ago, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't this Tooru's classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Tooru's like in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're all scared of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Tooru's a very good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:35.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always going berserk around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:42.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I always saw her as swinging around a bat, covering the room with blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she would...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, here are the handouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:55.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of boys wasn't right on the original, so I corrected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:00.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I guess I made a typo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,To-o-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It was only natural," you said! You're so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dependable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H3BC4F4&\pos(920,36)\fad(300,100)\3c&H3646D0&}Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my textbook. Can I read along in yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot my contacts today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4B00B2&\an9\bord0\fad(600,0)}Too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:05:00.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've always wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never had a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:08.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can get along, Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HD3B018&\3c&H1FBDEE&\pos(440,22)\fs60\fad(0,1200)}Toorun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me treat you to some juice as a sign of our new friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did you call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a nice surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a bit too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:59.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, Toorun! I brought more drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Toorun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Toorun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:45.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You have a pretty forehead. It's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run is talking to a weird-looking guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what is with that shirt pattern?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Could you tell me where the nurse's office is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new school nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he might have been dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:11.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said, "You have a pretty forehead. It's very nice."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that kind of weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A new school nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks kind of dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\c&H7C4C47&\3c&HEFEDE7&\fad(800,0)\pos(1194,620)}School Nurse\N Satou Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's the type that girls kind of like—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking to her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you again for earlier. You were very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come by the nurse's office sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep a special bed just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you're too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come by anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like something's moving—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act friendly with Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your name is Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I call you Run-chan, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very cute. Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kind of look like an urchin.\N How does Uni-chan sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks kind of down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kind of just helped an enemy in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:27.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your forehead is very cute, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:36.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So very... So very...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:47.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's time for my medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No music, no life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you got the limited edition color!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I really want one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is high tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of music do you listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still living a no music life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you haven't put anything on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:28.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to do all sorts of things, but I couldn't get music into it. I think it might be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:29.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H6981F3&\3c&H5F5962&\fad(400,400)}MD Stereo\N {\c&H2DD7F4&\3c&H655760&}It doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H5E39DA&\3c&H5A4D58&\fad(400,400)}Cassette Deck\N {\c&H3ED4EF&\3c&H66545F&}It doesn't work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(1060,36)\c&H24D5F5&\3c&H222EBE&\fad(400,400)}Like a TV
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(70,36)\c&H3F27E1&\3c&H1800B7&\fad(400,400)}hit {\c&H59EBFF&\3c&H1E09BF&}at a {\c&HFDFFA2&\3c&H4241F1&}45 degree {\c&H59EBFF&\3c&H1E09BF&}angle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.34,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:46.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing really worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that last one?! Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took it apart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was broken, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think an amateur could fix one of these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could do something else, like take it to a shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Nagi! It's not yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:03.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were mine, I would take you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:07.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm not broken, so you don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, you need to use a computer to put music on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why'd you buy one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but where do you go every break?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let go until you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-I was just kidding, Toorun! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry! Are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all stretched out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go back when I wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We can use it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where do you want to go? Yutaka will take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has P.E. next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.49,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HEDE8E4&\3c&H161210&\bord4}In the end,\N Tooru put music on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H34362F&\3c&H989492&}Occupied
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty weird for us to wear bloomers in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other schools use shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloomers are just another pair of underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put on underwear on top of another pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underwear on underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:29.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a class in underwear is just plain weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not panties, so it's not embarrassing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're freaking embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more embarrassing than wearing bloomers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:47.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you shout it like that, it sounds like you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start your warm-up exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we supposed to pull for this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it push?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Then on three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we were supposed to pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it, Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing this one right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:37.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep fooling around and you might get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:43.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:52.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Now for the next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun is watching Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something for Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Who can solve this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look eager to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yutaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Come up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try putting it outside instead of tucking it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not wearing any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, look! Yuuko-chan isn't wearing any!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Don't shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened, and you're wearing your P.E. uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tuck it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:39.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,a normal one piece dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:58.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's start class now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with warm-up exercises, so pair up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pair up with Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Miporin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to pair up with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka wants to pair up with Toorun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pair up with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pair up with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miporin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:44.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuuko, do you have a band-aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:50.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I scraped my knee when I fell down during P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good! We need to disinfect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the nurse's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:18:00.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Washing it off and putting a band-aid on it is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. What if it gets infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:08.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. And class is going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! I never thought anyone would be right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I had an attack and fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:44.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan! What happened—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sensei. I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:57.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.\N In fact it was an honor to be stepped on by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:03.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but it seems like you like Run a lot.\N What do you like about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:06.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... How she can just talk to anyone like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:09.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how she doesn't have any ulterior motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... she can cause pain without knowing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her forehead is pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her forehead width is the best,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come by anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like class already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. You can't take scrapes lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:39.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if Nurse Satou is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on the floor earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think he'll be okay by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a bit worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That nurse is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's dangerous about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,ha-has some weird interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that my forehead was pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He does seem dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.57,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun, can you help me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. What part do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll explain from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-san is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you not understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been repeating it over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! You do this here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wrong! You do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I would have given up a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you do this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miporin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka, you've been bothering Tooru-san too much recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about her, Tooru-san.\N You don't need to mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:19.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:43.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother Tooru-san like that! If you don't understand, ask me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:55.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of lonely now that she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that! I didn't think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:09.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru! Wait, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No more!
