Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:14.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy! Mercy...
