Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yutaka and Miporin are main characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's almost summer.
