Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:15.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before we change into our swimsuits, there's that painful tradition...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.13,0:24:17.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next A Channel: Kilograms.
